OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright at first, but
OL,6,Fquickly clouding over through the
OL,7,Fmorning as outbreaks of rain move in
OL,8,Ffrom the west. Turning breezier in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with some drier interludes
OL,10,Fat times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud will continue to
OL,13,Fthicken this evening as the rain turns
OL,14,Fheavier. Staying breezy and mild under
OL,15,Fthe thick blanket of cloud.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FBreezy and cloudy with
OL,18,Foutbreaks of drizzle at first, and
OL,19,Fperhaps a few brighter spells. Rain
OL,20,Fwill turn heavier for a time in the
OL,21,Fafternoon, before clearing to the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
